      <title>华尔街银行预测中国将迎来十年来最大幅度降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/wall-street-banks-predict-biggest-china-rate-cuts-in-a-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多家华尔街银行认为，随着政策制定者加大力度刺激增长、抑制通货紧缩，中国央行明年将进行十年来最大幅度的降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/wall-street-banks-predict-biggest-china-rate-cuts-in-a-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 00:59:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利王先生表示，中国企业盈利可能进一步低于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/morgan-stanley-s-wang-says-china-at-risk-of-more-earnings-misses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利表示，由于中国政府迄今采取的措施不足以扭转困扰经济的通货紧缩趋势，中国企业盈利可能继续令人失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-06/morgan-stanley-s-wang-says-china-at-risk-of-more-earnings-misses</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Dec 2024 00:49:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
